Title: 005: Computer Forensics, Fraud Analytics And Knowing When To Take A Break With Dmitry Korneev
Description:
In this session of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with Forensics Investigator Dmitry Korneev. You will learn about Computer Forensics, what Fraud Analytics actually is and we will discuss how to know when to take a break from work.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at https://www.superdatascience.com/5
